					Praying Mantis Power!
				</navigationLabel>
				<contentItems>
					<contentItem id="126">
						<title>
							
						</title>
						<text>
							You can never sneak up on a praying mantis. They are able to turn their heads nearly 180 degrees and have excellent eyesight.  Their eyes can see movement up to 60 feet (18 meters) away!
						</text>
