			</contentSection><contentSection id="2">
				<title>
					Food and Health
				</title>
				<navigationLabel>
					Food and Health
				</navigationLabel>
				<contentItems>
					<contentItem id="126">
						<title>
							
						</title>
						<text>
							Praying mantises are carnivorous insects. They will eat any live prey they can reach.  This includes insects, other mantises and even small lizards and frogs!
						</text>
