			</contentSection><contentSection id="3">
				<title>
					Home Base
				</title>
				<navigationLabel>
					Home Base
				</navigationLabel>
				<contentItems>
					<contentItem id="126">
						<title>
							
						</title>
						<text>
							Praying mantises live in tropical regions in North, Central and South America, Asia, Australia, and Africa. Some species &#8211; like those in North America &#8211; live in more temperate conditions, but only when it&#8217;s warm! During the colder months, the adults die off and their eggs overwinter so a new generation is born in the spring.
						</text>
