						</mediaItem>
					</contentItem>
				</contentItems>
			</contentSection><contentSection id="4">
				<title>
					Danger Alert
				</title>
				<navigationLabel>
					Danger Alert
				</navigationLabel>
				<contentItems>
					<contentItem id="126">
						<title>
							
						</title>
						<text>
							Mantises have to look out for many predators, like monkeys, frogs, lizards, birds, spiders, and hornets. They protect themselves using camouflage and even biting and hissing to fight off predators.
						</text>
